               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Mǝʿrāf, The Common of the Office (fols. 3ra-79vb)
 I-1) Wāzemā,
                     The Office of the Vigils (fols. 3ra-15ra)
 I-2) Mawaddǝs, The Sunday Office
                     (fols. 15ra-32va)
 I-3) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “Gate of light” (fols.
                     32vb-35rb)
 I-4) Sǝbḥāta nagh, The Office of Matins (fols. 35rb-35va),
                     incomplete
 I-5) Za-mawāʿǝla ʾaṣwām, The Office for Lent (fols.
                     35va-59va)
 I-6) ʾArʾǝstä mǝhǝlla [za-Dāwit], Rogation (fols.
                     59vb-71vb)
 I-7) Kǝśtat za-ʾaryām, The festive Office (fols.
                     71vb-79vb).
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
